María Casares https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mar%C3%ADa_Casares 0 María Casares (21 November 1922 – 22 November 1996) was a Spanish-French actress and one of the most distinguished stars of the French stage. She was usually credited in France as Maria Casarès. María_Casares ( 21 November_1922 – 22_November_1996 ) was a_Spanish-French_actress and one of the_most_distinguished_stars of the_French_stage .
